description:
MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

TNT trains and honey sweet plains... today we mess around with railcraft and beekeeping. 

FTB is currently in beta and is about to get a big update. New mods are getting added, world generation is changing, and a few other important changes are taking place with the mod pack. For this reason, we have decided to generate a new world map for MindCrack FTB when the update comes out.
